dequate use of weak and strong correlation\nfeatures identified by pre-trained \\textit{GBDT} models. Experimental results\non off-line data set and online deployment demonstrate the effectiveness of the\nproposed methods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 May 2018 02:22:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Aug 2018 04:14:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 19 Nov 2018 03:36:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-20"}
