ampling cost saving without knowing the best parameter setting in advance. The\nproposed trainer framework can be easily extended to other cases in which the\nhyper-parameter tuning is costly.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 May 2018 03:08:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 29 May 2018 09:14:20 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 27 Dec 2018 03:22:35 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 10 Mar 2019 05:13:36 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sat, 23 Mar 2019 13:45:03 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Wed, 5 Jun 2019 13:02:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-06"}
