usion regime, the\nBrownian-Bohmian motion shows a weak anomalous diffusion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 May 2018 07:50:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 28 May 2018 06:37:52 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 10 Jul 2018 09:44:01 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 7 Sep 2018 14:47:17 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 25 Sep 2018 05:56:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-26"}
