\%$ of relaxed massive clusters. This\nfraction increases to $\\sim$60$\\%$ for disturbed systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 May 2018 12:20:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-25"}
