ms. We also establish some relationships between the smallest Ritz values\nand these distances. Numerical experiments justify the sharpness of our\nresults.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 May 2018 07:23:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 24 Oct 2018 09:41:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 8 Jan 2019 04:23:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-20"}
